$ sudo vim /etc/logrotate.d/cronjob

Enter config lines in the file..

/home/gandalf/log/cron/mysqlcheck.log
/home/gandalf/log/cron/webbackup.log
/home/gandalf/log/cron/mysqlbackup.log
{
        su gandalf root
        rotate 7
       	weekly
       	missingok
        notifempty
        delaycompress
        compress
        copytruncate
        }

Test:
$ sudo logrotate -v -f /etc/logrotate.d/cronjob
